ntic Basin delaying their maintenance. If that is so, watch out for higher risks of unplanned outages as a consequence of pushing units to the operational limit.\n\n#oott", "time": "00:02", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 17573, "views": 12916, "likes": 118, "replies": 9, "retweets": 17, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 13, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062379293876051968", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2062379293876051984", "text": "Good morning. It’s day 96 of the war. From the WSJ: Trump has privately told aides he would consider ending the ceasefire if Iran kills U.S. troops, but for now is willing to tolerate ongoing low-level clashes to avoid a broader regional war. #OOTT", "time": "03:41", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 173868, "views": 19776, "likes": 142, "replies": 11, "retweets": 14, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062393686965490176", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062393686965490176", "text": "USDA has now confirmed the detection of a New World screwworm in a bovine in Zavala County, Texas. The detection of the parasite, which is deadly to cattle, comes at a dire time for the US beef industry, with a smaller herd having already sent prices to record highs.", "time": "04:39", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 78689, "likes": 411, "replies": 20, "retweets": 105, "quotes": 10, "bookmarks": 37, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062414355098988550", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062414355098988550", "text": "CHART OF THE DAY: Perhaps the most important story in global markets / geopolitics right now.\n\nChina's oil imports plunged to ~6.6m b/d in May, according to @Vortexa data, down ~38% vs 2025 average (or ~4m b/d).\n\nI wrote this @Opinion column in early May: https://t.co/XK71uh81m1 https://t.co/AnvT3xW", "time": "06:01", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 627073, "likes": 830, "replies": 67, "retweets": 211, "quotes": 47, "bookmarks": 231, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062431015537111531", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062431015537111531", "text": "From my @Opinion column:\n\n\"... make no mistake, China is rebalancing the oil market today. The bigger question is for tomorrow: If the country can reduce imports so drastically without, apparently, having to take extreme measures, what does that say about the future of oil consumption there? Nothing", "time": "07:07", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 28778, "likes": 271, "replies": 24, "retweets": 22, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 30, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062448514039214080", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062448514039214363", "text": "#Russia: oil production is lower now in comparison to the start of the year due to unplanned maintenances of oil refineries - deputy PM Novak #oott", "time": "08:16", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 6026, "likes": 17, "replies": 3, "retweets": 3, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 1, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062450108206141952", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062450108206141728", "text": "#Singapore: oil product inventories fell by 6.142mb w/w to 38.143mb last week #oott", "time": "08:23", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 92774, "likes": 140, "replies": 2, "retweets": 20, "quotes": 9, "bookmarks": 31, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062492811723735361", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062492811723735361", "text": "Despite the fertilizer scare and they hype of an imminent food crisis / famine, the price of wheat, corn and soybean is today LOWER than it was on Feb. 27.\n\nBut there are two farming stories worth paying attention (and bullish): screwworm detected in Texas and a strong El Niño.", "time": "11:13", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 163816, "likes": 622, "replies": 48, "retweets": 99, "quotes": 18, "bookmarks": 116, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062499033994739915", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062499033994739915", "text": "@climateconomics The oil price movement is perfectly rational", "time": "11:37", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 5568, "likes": 16, "replies": 8, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 3, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062504072792453351", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062504072792453351", "text": "Why I call the below the most important story in markets / geopolitics?\n\n1) without China importing far less, oil would be way, way above $100\n\n2) Fed would be forced to hike rates, crashing Wall Street \n\n3) President Trump would be against the clock in negotiations with Iran", "time": "11:57", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 277834, "likes": 1222, "replies": 93, "retweets": 292, "quotes": 23, "bookmarks": 314, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062518745839329469", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062518745839329469", "text": "No, no and no. The arrival of the New World Screwworm to the US has nothing to do with President Trump slashing foreign aid programs.\n\nIt was a when, rather than if, question its arrival to Texas since the screwworm jumped north the biological barrier of the Darién Gap in 2022.", "time": "12:56", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 121649, "likes": 324, "replies": 98, "retweets": 40, "quotes": 20, "bookmarks": 40, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062585952237723869", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062585952237723869", "text": "Of note: The cost of urea fertilizer in the US GoM (New Orleans benchmark) is down to pre-war levels of ~$470 per metric ton (down ~33% from a peak of ~$710 in mid-April). \n\nUrea prices also sharply lower (30-40% down) in Latam and Europe, although still above pre-war levels.", "time": "17:23", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 117615, "likes": 514, "replies": 34, "retweets": 100, "quotes": 10, "bookmarks": 109, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062601968166617088", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062601968166617428", "text": "Worth to be listened comments from the Saudi energy minister from the St Petersburg International Economic Forum earlier today #oott https://t.co/n85cUECwTK", "time": "18:26", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 66547, "likes": 201, "replies": 8, "retweets": 55, "quotes": 7, "bookmarks": 71, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062605717555618048", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2062605717555617922", "text": "Some more comments from the Saudi energy minister #oott https://t.co/Yy55wRNUEw", "time": "18:41", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "views": 29637, "likes": 54, "replies": 1, "retweets": 14, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 27, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062605751495906048", "url": "https://x.com/SheDrills/status/2062605751495905710", "text": "“Paper prices have disconnected from physical markets” #OOTT https://t.co/Y5qYumARCR", "time": "18:41", "author": "SheDrills", "author_name": "Christine Guerrero", "followers": 22707, "views": 15550, "likes": 129, "replies": 10, "retweets": 19, "quotes": 3, "bookmarks": 47, "labels": null}, {"id": "2062635078576902646", "url": "https://x.com/JavierBlas/status/2062635078576902646", "text": "More lessons learnt over ~100 days", "time": "20:38", "author": "JavierBlas", "author_name": "Javier Blas", "followers": 393796, "views": 48675, "likes": 103, "replies": 5, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": null}], "top_authors_by_tweets": [{"username": "staunovo", "name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 119641, "tweets": 40, "views": 286496, "likes": 679}, {"username": 